How To Use

To use Escape From Teck Neck , simply follow the 3 steps under the Start button.

Start

The first step requires you to select the sensitivity and position of the camera you are using. The sensitivity describes how sensitive our machine learning model we created is to your current posture, and for our model to correctly mesure your posture, it needs to know if you positioned your camera to the left- or right side of you.
